            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align:center">
                <h3>Medium</h3>
                <p>
                    - 99% Up-Time Guarantee
                </p>
                <p>
                    - Unlimited Storage
                </p>
                <p>
                    - RSR Bundle
                </p>
                <p>
                    - Up to 20 People
